<p><img style="float: right;" src="/images/logos/logo.COSI.BioVis.2022.png" width="100px">The BioVis track aims to educate, inspire, and engage bioinformatics and biology researchers in state-of-the-art visualization research and visualization researchers in problems in biological data visualization.</p>
