</td>
<td>
<p>This is a closed track, it is not accepting abstract submissions.</p>
<p>This industry workshop features three expert panels exploring how AI/ML is transforming bioinformatics across pharma, biotech, and venture capital. Leaders from AstraZeneca, Sanofi, 10X Genomics, Tempus AI, Google Ventures, Khosla Ventures, and Third Rock Ventures discuss real-world AI applications in drug discovery and genomics, talent requirements, and investment strategies. Each 30-minute panel includes interactive discussions on career opportunities and skills needed in computational biology. Ideal for researchers, data scientists, and bioinformatics professionals interested in industry careers or entrepreneurship</p>
